        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Check ClawHub trust before plugin installs",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nReapplies the ClawHub plugin-install trust check from #81307 after the revert in #81363.\n\nThis PR keeps the original trust-check scope:\n\n- check ClawHub exact-release trust before ClawHub plugin downloads\n- require interactive acknowledgement, or `--acknowledge-clawhub-risk`, for risky releases\n- warn for pending/stale clean trust records without requiring acknowledgement\n- fail closed when ClawHub security data is unavailable or malformed\n- keep the existing local dangerous-code scanner intact\n\nThis does not close or replace the later scanner-removal discussion/PR.\n\n## Rebase/current-main compatibility notes\n\nThis branch also carries narrow compatibility fixes needed after rebasing onto current `main`:\n\n- preserve plugin runtime config scope for both current mutation helpers and deprecated compatibility helpers\n- avoid deprecated Matrix test-runtime imports while keeping the local media mock behavior\n- apply the current gateway `sessions-patch` lint fix\n- refresh prompt snapshots for the current runtime prompt shape\n\n## Verification\n\n- `pnpm test src/infra/clawhub.test.ts src/plugins/clawhub.test.ts src/plugins/update.test.ts src/cli/clawhub-risk-acknowledgement.test.ts src/cli/plugins-cli.install.test.ts src/cli/plugins-cli.update.test.ts src/cli/update-cli.test.ts src/cli/update-cli/post-core-plugin-convergence.test.ts src/commands/onboarding-plugin-install.test.ts src/commands/doctor/repair-sequencing.test.ts src/commands/doctor/shared/missing-configured-plugin-install.test.ts src/auto-reply/reply/commands-plugins.install.test.ts src/auto-reply/reply/queue/settings.test.ts src/gateway/node-registry.test.ts src/gateway/node-connect-reconcile.test.ts src/gateway/sessions-patch.test.ts src/plugins/registry.runtime-config.test.ts extensions/matrix/src/matrix/monitor/media.test.ts extensions/matrix/src/approval-reactions.test.ts extensions/matrix/src/plugin-entry.runtime.test.ts src/plugins/contracts/deprecated-internal-config-api.test.ts src/plugins/contracts/plugin-sdk-package-contract-guardrails.test.ts`\n- `pnpm check:changed`\n- `pnpm docs:check-mdx`\n- `pnpm prompt:snapshots:check`\n- `NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=12288 pnpm build`\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`\n- `git diff --check`\n\nLocal CLI proof against a local ClawHub fixture/proxy also passed for clean, risky-unacknowledged, risky-acknowledged, and blocked trust responses.\n",
        "branch": "jesse/clawhub-install-trust-remake",
